I"Z<h1 id="rails项目的mvc目录结构">Rails项目的MVC目录结构</h1>

<p>object:
<strong>Model</strong>
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">app/models/object.rb</code></p>

<p><strong>Views</strong></p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>app/views/objects/index.html.erb
              /show
              /...
</code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>Controller</strong></p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>app/controllers/objects_controller.rb
   actions
   index
   show
   ...
</code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>Routes</strong></p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">config/routes.rb</code></p>

<p>map URI —&gt; controller#action
resource object —&gt; index, show, …</p>
